block vars
  - var activeLink = 'vue';
  - var title = 'Template7 Template Vue Component | Framework7 Vue Documentation';

block content

    .docs-nav
      include ../_docs-vue-menu
    .docs-content
      h1 Template7 Template Vue Component
      p Sometimes you may need to use <a href="http://idangero.us/template7/" target="_blank">Template7</a> templates, like in Virtual List component. For this case there is a special Vue component.
      h2 Usage example
      pre
        code
          :code
            <t7-template>
              <f7-card title="Title" :content="'Hello, {{name}}'" footer="Footer"></f7-card>
            </t7-template>
      p Renders to:
      pre
        code.html
          :code
            <script type="text/template7">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">Title</div>
                <div class="card-content">
                  <div class="card-content-inner">Hello, {{name}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">Footer</div>
              </div>
            </script>